      "content": "hey i am in so much pain rn. my lower back is killing me and i already took like 800mg of ibuprofen like an hour ago but it isnt doing anything. i really need to get some sleep. can i just take some aspirin on top of it or maybe a higher dose of the ibu to finally knock this pain out?",
